00:47:10.420 --> 00:47:14.350
has continued to evolve,
from increased connections

00:47:14.350 --> 00:47:17.160
that we've made after the fact
and additional information

00:47:17.160 --> 00:47:18.350
that we've learned.

00:47:18.350 --> 00:47:20.190
So seeing that,
actually, there are

00:47:20.190 --> 00:47:23.256
lots of opportunities to
remain engaged and follow up.

00:47:23.256 --> 00:47:25.920
MALE SPEAKER: So I
think, for me, there's

00:47:25.920 --> 00:47:29.490
probably two social
